Package: ROpenCVLite
Type: Package
Title: Helper Package for Installing OpenCV with R
Version: 4.51.0
Date: 2021-03-21
Authors@R: c( person("Simon", "Garnier", email = "garnier@njit.edu",
        role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID =
